step_data.thought:
I received a timeout error when trying to click on what I thought was a 'Page 2' link. Looking at the accessibility tree more carefully, I can see page navigation exists at elements [1967] through [1976]. Element [1975] shows I'm currently reading page 2, and [1971] shows a link to Page 1. So I'm already on page 2 of some product listings.
